            ],
            "ref_spans": [],
            "section": ""
        },
        {
            "text": "The current situation has changed, and another serious problem has risen. The stock of PPE was sufficient at the time of submission of our report [1] , but the PPE shortage has increased the risk of infection for the medical staff. The support of the government may be necessary to address this problem that confronts us.",
